StudentUsers: student_id, aubnet_id, email, first_name, last_name, dob, created_at, updated_at
RegisteredClubs: student_id (primary key, foreign key), club_id(primary key, foreign key), role
Posts: post_id (primary key), student_id
Upvotes:
